  <reg:content>
    <bcl:section id="d2e38">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Definition</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>In this regulation, <in:term>Act</in:term> means the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/11019_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Teachers Act</in:doc></bcl:link>.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e56">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Certification fee</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e64">
        <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>The following are the prescribed fees for the purposes of section 30 (1) (b) <in:desc>[issuance of certificate]</in:desc> of the Act that must accompany an applicant's application for a certificate of qualification or an independent school teaching certificate:</bcl:text>
        <bcl:paragraph id="d2e76">
          <bcl:num>a</bcl:num>
          <bcl:text>$245 for an applicant who has a degree in education from a post-secondary institution established in Canada;</bcl:text>
        </bcl:paragraph>
        <bcl:paragraph id="d2e85">
          <bcl:num>b</bcl:num>
          <bcl:text>$395 for an applicant who has a degree in education from a post-secondary institution established outside Canada;</bcl:text>
        </bcl:paragraph>
        <bcl:paragraph id="d2e95">
          <bcl:num>c</bcl:num>
          <bcl:text>$245 for an applicant who applies for a certificate of qualification or an independent school teaching certificate for which a degree in education from a post-secondary institution is not required by the certification standards or the independent school teaching certification standards.</bcl:text>
        </bcl:paragraph>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e104">
        <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>The following are the prescribed fees for the purposes of section 30 (1) (b) of the Act that an applicant must pay when the director of certification issues a certificate of qualification or an independent school teaching certificate:</bcl:text>
        <bcl:paragraph id="d2e113">
          <bcl:num>a</bcl:num>
          <bcl:text>$40 if the certificate of qualification or independent school teaching certificate is issued on or after December 1 and on or before May 31;</bcl:text>
        </bcl:paragraph>
        <bcl:paragraph id="d2e122">
          <bcl:num>b</bcl:num>
          <bcl:text>$80 if the certificate of qualification or independent school teaching certificate is issued on or after June 1 and on or before November 30.</bcl:text>
        </bcl:paragraph>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:hnote>[am. B.C. Reg. 14/2012, s. 1.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e135">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Repealed</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2.1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>Repealed. [B.C. Reg. 244/2011, s. 2.1 (3).]</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e147">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Reconsideration fee</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>3</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The prescribed reconsideration fee for the purposes of section 32 (3) (b) <in:desc>[reconsideration and appeal]</in:desc> of the Act is $140.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e162">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Certification appeal fee</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>4</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The certification appeal fee for the purposes of Division 5 <in:desc>[Certification Appeals]</in:desc> of Part 6 <in:desc>[Disciplinary and Professional Conduct Inquiries and Certification Appeals]</in:desc> of the Act is $300.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e181">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Letter of permission fee</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>5</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The prescribed letter of permission fee for the purposes of section 35 (1) (a) <in:desc>[issuance of letter of permission]</in:desc> of the Act is $200.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e196">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Annual practice fee</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>6</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The following are the prescribed fees for the purposes of section 37 <in:desc>[annual practice fee]</in:desc> of the Act:</bcl:text>
      <bcl:paragraph id="d2e210">
        <bcl:num>a</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>the annual practice fee is $80;</bcl:text>
      </bcl:paragraph>
      <bcl:paragraph id="d2e219">
        <bcl:num>b</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>the late fee under section 37 (2) of the Act is $30;</bcl:text>
      </bcl:paragraph>
      <bcl:paragraph id="d2e229">
        <bcl:num>c</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>the additional late fee under section 37 (3) (b) of the Act is $30.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:paragraph>
      <bcl:hnote>[en. B.C. Reg. 14/2012, s. 3.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e242">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Teacher education programs</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>7</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The fee for determining if a teacher education program meets the teacher education program approval standards is $12 000.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e254">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Fees for other services under the Act</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>8</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>The fee set out in Column 2 of the Table is prescribed for the service set out opposite in Column 1:</bcl:text>
      <oasis:table style="2">
        <oasis:tgroup cols="3">
          <oasis:tbody>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>Item</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>Column 1<in:br/><in:strong>Service</in:strong></oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c3" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>Column 2<in:br/><in:strong>Prescribed Fee</in:strong></oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>1</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2">
                <oasis:line>verification of a certificate of qualification</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c3" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>$35</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>2</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2">
                <oasis:line>re-evaluation of requirements for a certificate of qualification or an independent school teaching certificate</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c3" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>$35</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>3</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2">
                <oasis:line>statement of standing in relation to a certificate of qualification</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c3" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>$35</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>4</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2">
                <oasis:line>issuance of a printed certificate of qualification</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c3" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>$35</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>5</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2">
                <oasis:line>fee for forwarding a document in relation to a certificate of qualification</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c3" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>$35</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
            <oasis:trow>
              <oasis:entry colname="c1" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>6</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c2">
                <oasis:line>application for extension of a certificate of qualification</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
              <oasis:entry colname="c3" align="center" valign="top">
                <oasis:line>$35</oasis:line>
              </oasis:entry>
            </oasis:trow>
          </oasis:tbody>
        </oasis:tgroup>
      </oasis:table>
      <bcl:hnote>[am. B.C. Regs. 14/2012, s. 4; 75/2023, Sch. 1.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
